      "author": "VIktor (Viktor)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hello together, it is possible to change the group name of the subitems. Tried it using API. There is some success, but the group name is still retained. Are there other approaches to this?<br />\nThank you very much.<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/4/c/4c6e52f9b5091af5c14e72cf4d41efeb11b2bfaa.png\" title=\"Bildschirmfoto 2024-01-18 um 18.36.35\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/4/c/4c6e52f9b5091af5c14e72cf4d41efeb11b2bfaa_2_690x119.png\" alt=\"Bildschirmfoto 2024-01-18 um 18.36.35\" width=\"690\" height=\"119\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Bildschirmfoto 2024-01-18 um 18.36.35</span><span class=\"informations\">2036×354 121 KB</span></div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/0/d/0d1400be4cf36c561cf1152fcb36b1a76736b2b4.jpeg\" title=\"Bildschirmfoto 2024-01-18 um 18.25.22\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/0/d/0d1400be4cf36c561cf1152fcb36b1a76736b2b4_2_690x306.jpeg\" alt=\"Bildschirmfoto 2024-01-18 um 18.25.22\" width=\"690\" height=\"306\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Bildschirmfoto 2024-01-18 um 18.25.22</span><span class=\"informations\">1920×852 47.8 KB</span></div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/f/9/f9c08c66eeb6252e1b18cdc37b1c58b86e23e0db.jpeg\" title=\"Bildschirmfoto 2024-01-18 um 18.35.29\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/f/9/f9c08c66eeb6252e1b18cdc37b1c58b86e23e0db_2_690x161.jpeg\" alt=\"Bildschirmfoto 2024-01-18 um 18.35.29\" width=\"690\" height=\"161\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Bildschirmfoto 2024-01-18 um 18.35.29