      "createdAt": "2024-01-21T09:06:40.432Z",
      "author": "Matias.Monday (Matias)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hello there <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/viktor\">@VIktor</a>,</p>\n<p>Your mutation should change the title of the group in the subitems’ board.</p>\n<p>If you query for that title, you will probably see “Bestellungen”.</p>\n<p>You might need to refresh your browser to see the change. I just tested this and it is working correctly.</p>\n<p>Let me know if you have any other questions <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/slightly_smiling_face.png?v=12\" title=\":slightly_smiling_face:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slightly_smiling_face:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p>Cheers,<br />\nMatias</p>"
    },
