      "createdAt": "2024-01-21T17:41:06.789Z",
      "author": "VIktor (Viktor)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hello <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/matias.monday\">@Matias.Monday</a> , thanks for the answer.<br />\nUnfortunately it did not work, I tried again and reloaded the page. It just doesn’t change. Or is the new title anywhere else to see?<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/0/1/011ebb8322eb7c1fc558087c5b913d8cef0ff57b.jpeg\" title=\"Bildschirmfoto 2024-01-21 um 20.35.58\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/0/1/011ebb8322eb7c1fc558087c5b913d8cef0ff57b_2_690x202.jpeg\" alt=\"Bildschirmfoto 2024-01-21 um 20.35.58\" width=\"690\" height=\"202\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Bildschirmfoto 2024-01-21 um 20.35.58</span><span class=\"informations\">1920×564 42.8 KB</span></div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/0/8/082f3f9cf7ba6920696cfc1f5fe8318539f36a11.png\" title=\"Bildschirmfoto 2024-01-21 um 20.36.17\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/0/8/082f3f9cf7ba6920696cfc1f5fe8318539f36a11_2_690x220.png\" alt=\"Bildschirmfoto 2024-01-21 um 20.36.17\" width=\"690\" height=\"220\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Bildschirmfoto 2024-01-21 um 20.36.17</span><span class=\"informations\">2218×708 65.4 KB</span></div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/3/e/3e3ab318c8c0cd7663a070d0c7ad5b0e5252a1ff.jpeg\" title=\"Bildschirmfoto 2024-01-21 um 20.35.42\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/3/e/3e3ab318c8c0cd7663a070d0c7ad5b0e5252a1ff_2_690x142.jpeg\" alt=\"Bildschirmfoto 2024-01-21 um 20.35.42\" width=\"690\" height=\"142\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Bildschirmfoto 2